{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Do not use generic SaaS-style cards.
    Make it feel more like a real premium industrial-signage brand website: clean, confident, modern, technical, and visually strong.
    
    Section goal:
    Show the pole sign installation process in a way that feels trustworthy, professional, and impressive for potential customers.
    
    Design direction:
    - modern corporate-industrial style
    - premium but practical
    - strong visual hierarchy
    - clean layout with bold typography
    - inspired by a real signage / printing / installation company website
    - more brand-driven and less template-like
    
    Layout concept:
    Create a horizontal process timeline section instead of simple floating cards.
    
    Suggested structure:
    - strong section heading at the top
    - short supporting subtitle
    - below that, a wide horizontal visual timeline
    - each step should feel connected as part of one real installation journey
    - use large real-photo thumbnails with consistent aspect ratio
    - content should feel more integrated, not like separate random cards
    
    Visual style:
    - white, soft grey, and brand blue / cyan accents
    - subtle industrial feel
    - clean background with structured spacing
    - use thin lines, dividers, or timeline connectors between steps
    - avoid overly rounded playful UI
    - reduce “app UI” feeling
    - make it feel like a premium company profile website
    
    For each step:
    - large image
    - step title
    - short technical caption
    - optional small text link: “View service” or “See more”
    - no floating number badges
    - instead, use a more elegant step label treatment such as:
      - small top caption
      - timeline marker dot
      - or inline numbering integrated into the layout
    
    Important interaction changes:
    - replace the bottom scrollbar with elegant navigation dots
    - centered dot pagination below the process slider
    - active dot in brand accent colour
    - smooth slide transition
    - swipe on mobile
    - click dots to navigate
    
    Make the section more visually engaging by:
    - using strong photography first
    - using a connected timeline layout
    - adding subtle hover motion only
    - slight image zoom on hover
    - soft overlay on image hover
    - smooth fade-up entrance animation on scroll
    
    Typography:
    - bold clean heading
    - refined subheading
    - step titles should feel confident and technical
    - body text should be lighter and smaller
    
    Overall feeling:
    - premium signage company
    - engineering credibility
    - installation expertise
    - custom production capability
    - not playful, not cute, not generic
    - should feel suitable for a company that handles signage, metal letters, lightboxes, printing, and nationwide installation
    
    Optional bottom row:
    Add a thin trust-info row under the slider with items like:
    - Custom Production
    - Nationwide Installation
    - Professional Team
    - Engineering Support
    
    Do not make it look too minimal or too empty.
    Do not make it too decorative either.
    Balance brand strength, clarity, and premium presentation., Refine the layout to ensure perfect center alignment and proper mobile responsiveness.
    
    1. Center alignment (important)
    - The entire section content must be perfectly centered within a max-width container
    - Use a fixed max-width (e.g. 1200px–1320px)
    - Center with margin: 0 auto
    - Ensure title, subtitle, and cards align to the same center axis
    - Remove any uneven left/right spacing
    
    2. Card layout (desktop)
    - Use a clean grid: 3 columns (not stretched)
    - Gap between cards: 24–32px
    - Cards must stay centered even if there are only 2–3 items
    - Do NOT justify space-between
    - Use justify-content: center
    
    3. Mobile responsive (very important)
    - Switch to horizontal scroll (carousel style) on mobile
    - Show 1.2–1.4 cards per view (so user knows it can swipe)
    - Add padding left/right (16–20px)
    - Smooth scroll with snap (scroll-snap-type: x mandatory)
    
    4. Dot navigation (mobile + desktop)
    - Center the dots below the cards
    - Keep spacing tight and clean
    - Active dot in brand color
    - Dots must align perfectly center with section
    
    5. Image + text alignment
    - Image, title, and description must align vertically
    - Keep consistent padding inside cards
    - Avoid text shifting or uneven heights
    
    6. Section spacing
    - Top & bottom padding: 80–120px desktop / 48–64px mobile
    - Keep breathing space but not too empty
    
    7. Overall feel
    - Balanced, centered, clean
    - No floating or misaligned elements
    - Feels like a professional company website, not a template
    
    Do not change content or structure.
    Only fix layout, alignment, spacing, and responsiveness.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-process-timeline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subheading_color }};
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-slider-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 28px;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-marker-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.border_color }};
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-process-timeline-step-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-image-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
    transition: background-color 0.4s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-process-timeline-step-image-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.step_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.step_title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-caption-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.step_caption_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.step_caption_color }};
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-step-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}::after {
    content: '→';
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.border_color }};
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    width: 28px;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-trust-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 50px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid {{ block.settings.border_color }};
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: {{ block.settings.step_caption_color }};
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-process-timeline-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-process-timeline-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.heading_size }}px * 0.75);
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-trust-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.7 }}px 0 {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-process-timeline-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-slider-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      overflow-x: auto;
      overflow-y: hidden;
      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      scrollbar-width: none;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-slider-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      grid-template-columns: none;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 20px 20px 20px 20px;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-step-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 82%;
      min-width: 82%;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.heading_size }}px * 0.65);
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-trust-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: 20px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      padding-right: 20px;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.6 }}px 0 {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-process-timeline-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<installation-process-{{ ai_gen_id }}
  class="ai-process-timeline-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
  {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
>
  <div class="ai-process-timeline-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank or block.settings.subheading != blank %}
      <div class="ai-process-timeline-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-process-timeline-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.subheading != blank %}
          <p class="ai-process-timeline-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subheading }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-process-timeline-slider-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-process-timeline-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slider>
        {% for i in (1..6) %}
          {% liquid
            assign step_enabled_key = 'step_' | append: i | append: '_enabled'
            assign step_label_key = 'step_' | append: i | append: '_label'
            assign step_image_key = 'step_' | append: i | append: '_image'
            assign step_title_key = 'step_' | append: i | append: '_title'
            assign step_caption_key = 'step_' | append: i | append: '_caption'
            assign step_link_text_key = 'step_' | append: i | append: '_link_text'
            assign step_link_url_key = 'step_' | append: i | append: '_link_url'

            assign step_enabled = block.settings[step_enabled_key]
            assign step_label = block.settings[step_label_key]
            assign step_image = block.settings[step_image_key]
            assign step_title = block.settings[step_title_key]
            assign step_caption = block.settings[step_caption_key]
            assign step_link_text = block.settings[step_link_text_key]
            assign step_link_url = block.settings[step_link_url_key]
          %}

          {% if step_enabled %}
            <div class="ai-process-timeline-step-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-step="{{ i }}">
              <div class="ai-process-timeline-step-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if step_label != blank %}
                  <div class="ai-process-timeline-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <span class="ai-process-timeline-step-marker-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></span>
                    {{ step_label }}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="ai-process-timeline-step-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if step_image %}
                    <img
                      src="{{ step_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                      alt="{{ step_image.alt | escape }}"
                      loading="lazy"
                      width="{{ step_image.width }}"
                      height="{{ step_image.height }}"
                      class="ai-process-timeline-step-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                    >
                    <div class="ai-process-timeline-step-image-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
                  {% else %}
                    <div class="ai-process-timeline-step-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>

                {% if step_title != blank %}
                  <h3 class="ai-process-timeline-step-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ step_title }}</h3>
                {% endif %}

                {% if step_caption != blank %}
                  <p class="ai-process-timeline-step-caption-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ step_caption }}</p>
                {% endif %}

                {% if step_link_text != blank and step_link_url != blank %}
                  <a
                    href="{{ step_link_url }}"
                    class="ai-process-timeline-step-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  >
                    {{ step_link_text }}
                  </a>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-process-timeline-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-dots></div>

    {% if block.settings.show_trust_row %}
      <div class="ai-process-timeline-trust-row-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.trust_item_1 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-process-timeline-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <svg class="ai-process-timeline-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            {{ block.settings.trust_item_1 }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.trust_item_2 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-process-timeline-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <svg class="ai-process-timeline-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            {{ block.settings.trust_item_2 }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.trust_item_3 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-process-timeline-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <svg class="ai-process-timeline-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            {{ block.settings.trust_item_3 }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.trust_item_4 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-process-timeline-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <svg class="ai-process-timeline-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            {{ block.settings.trust_item_4 }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</installation-process-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class InstallationProcess{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.currentSlide = 0;
        this.slider = null;
        this.sliderWrapper = null;
        this.dots = null;
        this.steps = [];
        this.isMobile = false;
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.slider = this.querySelector('[data-slider]');
        this.sliderWrapper = this.querySelector('.ai-process-timeline-slider-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.dotsContainer = this.querySelector('[data-dots]');
        this.steps = Array.from(this.querySelectorAll('.ai-process-timeline-step-{{ ai_gen_id }}'));

        if (!this.slider || this.steps.length === 0) return;

        this.checkMobile();
        this.createDots();
        this.updateDots();

        window.addEventListener('resize', this.handleResize.bind(this));
        
        if (this.isMobile && this.sliderWrapper) {
          this.sliderWrapper.addEventListener('scroll', this.handleScroll.bind(this), { passive: true });
        }
      }

      checkMobile() {
        this.isMobile = window.innerWidth <= 749;
      }

      createDots() {
        if (!this.dotsContainer) return;

        this.dotsContainer.innerHTML = '';
        const totalDots = this.steps.length;

        for (let i = 0; i < totalDots; i++) {
          const dot = document.createElement('button');
          dot.classList.add('ai-process-timeline-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
          dot.setAttribute('aria-label', 'Go to slide ' + (i + 1));
          if (i === 0) dot.classList.add('active');

          dot.addEventListener('click', () => {
            this.scrollToSlide(i);
          });

          this.dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);
        }

        this.dots = Array.from(this.dotsContainer.querySelectorAll('.ai-process-timeline-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}'));
      }

      scrollToSlide(index) {
        if (!this.isMobile || !this.sliderWrapper) return;

        const step = this.steps[index];
        if (step) {
          const scrollLeft = step.offsetLeft - 20;
          this.sliderWrapper.scrollTo({
            left: scrollLeft,
            behavior: 'smooth'
          });
        }
      }

      handleScroll() {
        if (!this.isMobile || !this.sliderWrapper) return;

        const scrollLeft = this.sliderWrapper.scrollLeft;
        const stepWidth = this.steps[0].offsetWidth;
        const gap = 16;
        const currentIndex = Math.round(scrollLeft / (stepWidth + gap));

        if (currentIndex !== this.currentSlide) {
          this.currentSlide = currentIndex;
          this.updateDots();
        }
      }

      updateDots() {
        if (!this.dots) return;

        this.dots.forEach((dot, index) => {
          if (index === this.currentSlide) {
            dot.classList.add('active');
          } else {
            dot.classList.remove('active');
          }
        });
      }

      handleResize() {
        const wasMobile = this.isMobile;
        this.checkMobile();

        if (wasMobile !== this.isMobile) {
          this.currentSlide = 0;
          this.updateDots();
          
          if (this.isMobile && this.sliderWrapper) {
            this.sliderWrapper.scrollTo({ left: 0 });
          }
        }
      }

      disconnectedCallback() {
        window.removeEventListener('resize', this.handleResize.bind(this));
        if (this.sliderWrapper) {
          this.sliderWrapper.removeEventListener('scroll', this.handleScroll.bind(this));
        }
      }
    }

    customElements.define('installation-process-{{ ai_gen_id }}', InstallationProcess{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Process timeline",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Section heading"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Professional Installation Process"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "subheading",
      "label": "Subheading",
      "default": "From design consultation to final installation, our experienced team ensures precision and quality at every step"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "heading_size",
      "label": "Heading size",
      "min": 20,
      "max": 60,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 40
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "subheading_size",
      "label": "Subheading size",
      "min": 12,
      "max": 24,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 16
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Step 1"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "step_1_enabled",
      "label": "Enable step 1",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "step_1_label",
      "label": "Step label",
      "default": "Step 01"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "step_1_image",
      "label": "Image"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "step_1_title",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "Site Survey & Consultation"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "step_1_caption",
      "label": "Caption",
      "default": "Technical assessment and measurement of installation location"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "step_1_link_text",
      "label": "Link text"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "step_1_link_url",
      "label": "Link URL"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Step 2"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "step_2_enabled",
      "label": "Enable step 2",
